replies.body:
Riot is catering to new/casual players for money and killing their original fan base of gamers with overly oppressive bans and rules.

You can get matched up in ranked with a duo of 9 year olds, a blind guy, and a dog stuck to a keyboard, but say 'noob' and you get perm banned. Clown world.
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
